      <p>These jungle <a href="ch73s11.html#MonstersAnimals35">cats</a> are about 4 feet long and weigh about 120 pounds. They usually hunt at night. The statistics presented here can describe any feline of similar size, such as jaguars, panthers, and mountain <a href="ch73s24.html#MonstersAnimals84">lions</a>.</p>
